\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14045772\charrsid2650350 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13519019\charrsid2650350 They were within a reasonable distance?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2650350 AT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13519019\charrsid2650350 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14045772\charrsid2650350 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13519019\charrsid2650350 How much did you see of relatives?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2650350 AT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13519019\charrsid2650350 
Oh, I think quite a lot really. You were never - you never estranged from them - my - my mother w
ent to see one sister - one week and the sister came to see her the next week - that sister had a lot of children, she lived in Everton so we - she wasn't quite as free and I remember she used to come late but the trams ran 'til after twelve you know and 
we weren't an early family. So she was always there - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14045772\charrsid2650350 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13519019\charrsid2650350 You mentioned your mother had a lot of friends?
