Yes, yes. Yes. But - my mother wasn't one for running in and out other peoples houses but - we were always very friendly with our neighbours. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14045772\charrsid2650350 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13519019\charrsid2650350 What did your parents do
 when they got together with their friends or neighbours. - you mentioned you had a lot of musical evenings?
\par 
