Mary was - was lowere working class. And - and - I think perhaps there was upper working class - I can't think of anybody at the minute and then I think my mother - Mary would call themselves lower middle class. But I call myself upper - working class.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14045772\charrsid2650350 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13519019\charrsid2650350 This is what you feel now what you felt then?
