and then after that they - they - after I left and quite a few of them left they were - we }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5077625\charrsid2650350 weren\rquote t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13519019\charrsid2650350 ' the type that was used to this - we were in a big concrete shed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14045772\charrsid2650350 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13519019\charrsid2650350 And it was heavy going?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2650350 AT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13519019\charrsid2650350 It was heavy and it was - cold and damp. And we were the
re all winter. Yes. I was there 'til - I was there all over the winter into the summer. And then of course there was the flu epidemic - it was - April the epidemic - not the bad one - yes. And I got the flu - well we all did really, and then the doctor st
opped me going.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14045772\charrsid2650350 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13519019\charrsid2650350 So what did you do then?
