Oh I stayed home for quite a bit then and then in 1917 - early 1917 I - applied to go in a shipping office and I went there in 1917 and I loved it. It was book keeping.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14045772\charrsid2650350 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13519019\charrsid2650350 It wasn't boring this time?
