Oh, oh it was lovely. You had so many different things you could do. And I could do the lot - yes, it was easy. Interesting - yes, very interesting. Yes, all the boats getting - all - you had to do all the accounts for all the boats that they had Harris
on line - had a lot of boats. Oh it was wonderful.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14045772\charrsid2650350 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13519019\charrsid2650350 How did you get that job?
